Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.93,0:00:16.00,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Go get 'em, Mangoku! {she's a big fan of him}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.33,0:00:17.71,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it! Go for it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.55,0:00:31.04,IntroLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,These feelings I want to tell you are so heavy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.51,0:00:37.14,IntroLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I'll be flattened down
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.64,0:00:45.65,IntroLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,So many feelings I can't describe into words
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.65,0:00:50.29,IntroLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,It just won't reach, to that special person
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.79,0:00:53.04,IntroLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,This short yet very far distance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.91,0:00:57.54,IntroLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is always blue,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.12,0:01:01.96,IntroLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,But you just can't keep staring at it
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.04,0:01:05.38,IntroLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Round n' round, spinning Round n' Round
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.63,0:01:09.09,IntroLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Round n' round, spinning Round n' Round
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.58,0:01:13.06,IntroLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,You, who always pretend to be tottering
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.06,0:01:16.60,IntroLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to jump onto your chest
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.68,0:01:20.11,IntroLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Round n' round, spinning Round n' Round
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.35,0:01:23.69,IntroLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Round n' round, spinning Round n' Round
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.24,0:01:27.23,IntroLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Rising softly into the air,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.24,0:01:33.40,IntroLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I am drifting above the clouds again today!
