Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.05,0:01:53.50,IntroText,Sponsors,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1.6\be0\an8}Yagami High School, on spring field trip.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.52,0:01:58.05,IntroText,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1.6\be0\an8}Tsukamoto Tenma, snack allowance of 500 yen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.18,0:02:07.93,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,It's a great day for a field trip.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.31,0:02:12.67,SR-Main,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Field trip eh? Brings back memories of my elementary school days.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.67,0:02:16.45,SR-Main,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,At our age, I wouldn't call it a field trip. It's more like "Recreation".
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.54,0:02:18.58,SR-Main,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see much of a difference.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.67,0:02:21.65,SR-Main,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,So where are we going today?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.65,0:02:22.67,SR-Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.14,0:02:26.30,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,It's Karasuma-kun!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.72,0:02:29.01,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks kinda special today!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.34,0:02:30.50,SR-Main,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no kidding...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.90,0:02:41.54,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why snacks are so tasty on days like this? It feels different somehow!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.54,0:02:44.53,SR-Main,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna change seats once the bus leaves?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.68,0:02:47.10,SR-Main,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to be good ambience today.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.68,SR-Main,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Makes me wanna start conversations with boys I don't know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.82,0:02:51.57,SR-Main,MIkoto,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll pass on that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.33,0:02:56.46,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Alright, I'm definitely gonna sit next to Karasuma-kun!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.05,0:03:06.97,SR-Main,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan, the way you eat snacks and stuff... is heavenly.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.05,0:03:10.21,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I must sit next to you today!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.15,0:03:13.91,SR-Main,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,You eat like a squirrel...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.60,0:02:56.60,SR-notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\b1\bord1.8\fs26}Note:{\b0} She is snacking on "Pocky", a very popular Japanese stick snack with chocolate topping. Yummy~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.91,0:03:15.88,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit nervous...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.33,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Karasuma-kun!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.75,0:03:26.04,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I will do my best!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.71,0:03:41.42,SR-Main,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!! Why am I playing this card game with him? {Mokumoku to Baba Nuki is some Jap card game}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.68,0:03:44.31,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan is sitting right there!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.89,0:03:48.90,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And this guy is damn good! I can't read his expression at all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.89,0:03:48.90,SR-notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\b1\bord1.8\fs26}Note: {\b0}This is a card game where you need to trick your opponent into getting the joker.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.56,0:03:50.14,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.39,0:03:52.46,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really see Karasuma-kun from here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.70,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And to think I've gotten this close to him...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.70,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun, please move...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.05,0:04:02.54,SR-Main,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Argh! Why do I face away from Tenma-chan like this?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.58,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! I got the Joker again!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.95,0:04:10.49,SR-Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Alright bathroom break. Please be back in 15 minutes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.81,0:04:12.19,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.02,0:04:20.72,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Freakin' hell!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.43,SR-Main,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Goddammit! What have I done?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.92,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, it's ok. There are still plenty of chances.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.48,0:04:38.10,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for today, I've prepared all kinds of things to talk about.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.55,0:04:43.04,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I read a bunch of magazines too. There will be no mistakes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.84,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely sit next to you today, Tenma-chan!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.20,0:04:50.43,SR-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,The bus is departing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.70,0:04:51.71,SR-Main,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, gotta go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.87,0:04:58.87,SR-notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\b1\bord1.8\fs24}Sign{\b0}: "Sugaa mo Red Bread Elderly's Community", \Nor better translated as Peaceful Garden Graveyard Expedition. \N\N{\be}Pun{\b0}: Sugamo Jizo is a street where many OLD and ELDERLY ladies hang out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.68,SR-Main,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HDAC2BA&}This is the wrong bus...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.87,0:05:05.09,SR-Main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fnPrototype\bord0.5\3c&H0&\fs50\move(500,2,300,2)\c&HF0F0F&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\be1\an8}This is the wrong bus...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.91,0:05:01.09,SR-Main,Old lady,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HCFCFCF&}Oh my, what a handsome young lad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.99,SR-Main,Old guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HCFCFCF&}Kiddo, don't be concerned with Shiru-san. She's always like that. {text from manga: yoppodo no koto ja zo}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.76,0:05:08.80,SR-Main,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HDAC2BA&}I can't take this! And this old man is too damn good!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.03,0:05:11.51,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HDAC2BA&}I shouldn't be doing this here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.03,0:05:14.53,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HDAC2BA&}Driver, please stop the bus!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.57,SR-Main,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HCFCFCF&}What the... the match is not over yet!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.57,0:05:20.60,SR-Main,Old lady,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HCFCFCF&}Dear! You don't have to leave yet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.07,0:05:22.87,SR-Main,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HDAC2BA&}But I have to go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.87,0:05:24.59,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HDAC2BA&}Plea... Please let me go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.38,0:05:29.60,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HDAC2BA&}Tenma-chan!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.19,0:05:34.16,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.49,0:05:36.05,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.10,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get back on the school bus!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.36,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.20,0:05:48.27,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one, no one! No one at all! Which means...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.48,0:05:50.97,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chance!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.92,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what should I talk about?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.38,0:05:56.96,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I just want to have a chat with you, Karasuma-kun".
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.65,0:06:00.78,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...but that's kinda obvious isn't it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.58,0:06:03.48,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! I'm having fun here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.85,0:06:06.30,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, that's wrong too...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.73,0:06:13.51,SR-Main,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, Tenma's so vexing!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.02,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.42,0:06:21.00,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.28,0:06:22.25,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to do it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.49,0:06:26.81,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,K...Ka...Ka...Ka...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.81,0:06:28.30,SR-Main,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Karasuma-kun!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.30,0:06:29.29,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,May I?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.22,0:06:31.72,SR-Main,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.62,SR-Main,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.50,0:06:36.26,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,SO mean!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.78,0:06:40.22,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall feel my wrath of love!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.57,0:06:42.18,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shake her chair...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.41,0:06:47.08,SR-Main,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,This bus is shaking a lot...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.85,0:06:53.82,SR-Main,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamit! I must be with Tenma-chan!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.66,0:06:56.91,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I must get back on the bus, no matter what!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.53,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chaaa-
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.12,0:07:07.13,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan, I'm coming back now!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.77,SR-Main,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Strange, I feel sick...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.38,0:07:18.58,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, can I sit up front?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.17,0:07:20.63,SR-Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Bus sick?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.23,0:07:23.05,SR-Main,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,See ya later, Karasuma-kun.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.80,0:07:29.86,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Victory!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.83,0:07:34.86,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! This moment has finally arrived!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.51,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I feel sick too...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.51,0:07:38.80,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even more than Eri-chan.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.42,0:07:42.68,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be karma!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.26,0:07:47.77,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, can I sit up front too?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.13,0:07:49.89,SR-Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto, you too?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.18,SR-Main,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Are those two alright?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.43,0:07:53.18,SR-Main,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.56,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I will not give up yet!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.97,0:08:03.20,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will sit next to her!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.51,0:08:08.10,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan, wait for me!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.46,0:08:14.49,SR-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBFBFBF&}No one knows why.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.47,0:08:20.10,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBFBFBF&}All of a sudden, when she least expected it, she came to have this special power.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.47,0:08:29.49,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.90,0:08:34.60,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Good morning, Nee-san.  Breakfast is ready. Your bento is over there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.90,0:08:34.90,SR-notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\b1\bord1.8\fs26}Translator's Note: {\b0}"bento" or "obentou" is a Japanese lunch box with all kinds of delicious things inside.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.97,0:08:37.93,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be leaving early today.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.65,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? How unusual.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.94,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? There are 3 bentos...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.98,0:08:47.61,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,One for Yakumo, one for me, and...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.06,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be for someone she likes?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.57,0:08:56.60,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! Hurray! Fight Yakumo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.41,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.83,0:09:04.77,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Yakumo is finally in love...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.26,0:09:06.97,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will lovingly watch you from afar. {unless you know a better way to trans: atatakaku mimamotte ageyo}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.25,0:09:10.24,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But unlike me she's very naive.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.96,0:09:13.13,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What if she's being tricked by some bad guy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.04,0:09:18.19,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried. I'll sneak up and at least find out who he is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.63,0:09:20.19,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, forgot to lock up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.33,0:09:35.13,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.41,0:09:37.95,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,What? The bento was for a cat?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.46,0:09:40.81,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really thought you were in love.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.53,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Carp? No its a cat. {Yup, manga says koi:carp}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.90,0:09:45.90,SR-notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\b1\bord1.8\fs24}Translator's Note: {\b0}"Koi" means love in the conventional sense, but also means the fish species, carp. Same pronounciation but different kanji spelling.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.92,0:09:44.64,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,N... nevermind.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.22,0:09:47.06,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? A stray cat?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.72,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been taking care of it all this time?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.29,0:09:50.90,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.42,0:09:55.88,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, it's ignoring us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.13,0:09:58.80,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't trust me yet...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.23,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,A cat trying to act tough!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.50,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,He's being cautious.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.31,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the bentou here okay?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.31,0:10:07.77,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat it when you want to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.63,0:10:12.01,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, Yakumo! Why do you bother with this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.99,0:10:15.66,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to find out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.83,0:10:21.16,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget about some cat and try to get a guy or something!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.46,0:10:23.90,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack we're late! Let's go Yakumo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.37,0:10:25.90,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, okay?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.20,SR-Main,guy1,0000,0000,0000,,Hey check it out!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.18,0:10:36.79,SR-Main,guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Tsukamoto from 1st year?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.79,0:10:37.87,SR-Main,guy3,0000,0000,0000,,She is so cute!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.49,SR-Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,For real. She's got style too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.52,0:10:41.81,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she is the most popular girl of this year's freshies. {you decide}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.85,0:10:42.96,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, for sure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.78,0:10:48.45,SR-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just the looks, I tell you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.86,0:10:50.43,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's athletic as well.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.05,0:10:54.37,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Once, the track and field teacher wanted to recruit her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.33,0:10:57.15,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's smart.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.66,0:10:59.80,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She ranked 8 on her midterm exam.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.44,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,An ideal girl like that really exists huh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.47,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She is definitely popular with guys eh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.47,0:11:10.06,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, she doesn't seem to get involved with guys at all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.55,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's really picky? {Perhaps she feels its annoying?}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.55,0:11:15.62,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. Apparently, she just doesn't know how popular she is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.14,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a waste...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.31,0:11:21.61,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto Yakumo... you can say that's her only weakness.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.09,0:11:30.92,SR-Main,Sara,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.88,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Sara... Good morning.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.03,0:11:34.90,SR-Main,Sara,0000,0000,0000,,You seem so out of it. What's up?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.90,0:11:37.03,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,I think I just saw a cat.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.44,0:11:38.19,SR-Main,Sara,0000,0000,0000,,Cat?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.79,0:11:43.15,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... so it's that black cat huh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.62,0:11:44.75,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.11,0:11:50.72,SR-Main,Sara,0000,0000,0000,,A cat came to return the favor... that sounds like a fairy tale!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.97,0:11:56.07,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.  It's not... possible.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.51,0:12:03.13,SR-Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Got it? This part will be on the test.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.46,0:12:05.69,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So please write it down in your notes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.98,0:12:10.84,SR-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBFBFBF&}That day, Yakumo was a bit different from usual, to say the least.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.11,0:12:15.11,SR-Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pick it up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.00,0:12:21.61,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\move(650,2,300,2)\q2\fnShannon\c&HF0F0F&\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\be1\an8}Oh! First contact with Tsukamoto! Today is my lucky day!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.00,0:12:21.55,SR-Main,Thought&text&voice,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! First contact with Tsukamoto! Today is my lucky day!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.12,0:12:27.93,SR-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBFBFBF&}In other words, she is able to hear the thoughts from guys who like or are interested in her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.20,0:12:30.54,SR-Main,yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.98,0:12:33.38,SR-Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,YES! I gave her a good impression!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.27,0:12:40.22,SR-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBFBFBF&}But it proved useless to Yakumo whose heart has never been moved. {Renai onchi: She's clumsy/tone-deaf in areas of love}
