Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.93,0:12:54.13,SR-Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto-san right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.49,0:12:56.80,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a hard working and responsible person.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.22,0:13:01.15,SR-Main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fnShannon\c&HF0F0F&}{\move(600,2,200,2)\q2\bord1.5\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\be1\an8}Yeah whatever, muahahaha. Time to move in! I'll make her an adult.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.38,SR-Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you like to join the Student Council?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.38,0:13:04.11,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure you will help out for the school's sake right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.38,0:13:08.70,SR-Main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnShannon\c&HF0F0F&}{\move(650,2,300,2)\q2\bord1.5\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\be1\an8}After the sun sets, just the two of us in the classroom!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.97,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,But I... have to go home early.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.07,0:13:11.84,SR-Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well how 'bout a quick look at the student council room?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.74,0:13:14.00,SR-Main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fnShannon\c&HF0F0F&}{\move(650,2,300,2)\q2\bord1.5\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\be1\an8}Just the two of us... Just the two of us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.17,0:13:13.98,SR-Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Let's go! let's go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.52,0:13:17.12,SR-Main,Hanai,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You are scaring her.
