Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.89,0:13:27.45,SR-Main,text&voice,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Hanai Haruki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.88,SR-Main,hanai,0000,0000,0000,,I am the head of the Aikidou club.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.14,0:13:37.02,SR-Main,text&voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\fnShannon\c&HF0F0F&}{\move(550,2,350,2)\q2\bord1.5\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\be1\an8}Do you want to do Aikidou?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.43,0:13:32.40,SR-Main,hanai,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I am your sister Tsukamoto-kun's classmate. {explain about the -kun?}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.46,0:13:36.62,SR-Main,Text & Voice,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be straight to the point. Would you like to join the Aikidou club?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.60,0:13:40.82,SR-Main,hanai,0000,0000,0000,,I... want to see you wearing a hakama! {hakama: martial arts uniform}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.64,0:13:41.02,SR-Main,text&voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\fnShannon\c&HF0F0F&}{\move(550,2,350,2)\q2\bord1.5\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\be1\an8}I want to see you in a hakama!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.25,0:13:44.89,SR-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBFBFBF&}Admirably, here is a guy who thinks and speaks the same.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.49,0:13:48.60,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBFBFBF&}For Yakumo, this is the first guy to ever do so.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.27,0:13:52.36,SR-Main,yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... I'm not interested in martial arts.
