Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.14,0:14:20.70,SR-Main,hanai,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, this time for sure...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.98,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the? I can't even lay a finger on you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.23,0:14:35.32,SR-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBFBFBF&}Of course if you can read his mind, you can also easily dodge him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.66,0:14:39.33,SR-Main,hanai,0000,0000,0000,,Argh! To think her sister is a complete klutz!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.75,0:14:46.10,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.82,0:14:51.39,SR-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBFBFBF&}When someone speaks ill of her sister, Yakumo gets serious, quickly.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.72,0:15:04.41,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo! The stove! {explain the nabe?}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.12,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.62,0:15:18.64,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo! We should try something different today.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.88,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? I was gonna make curry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.50,0:15:25.01,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's try making a different kind of curry then!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.72,0:15:25.21,SR-Main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnShannon\c&HF0F0F&}{\move(430,2,380,2)\q2\bord1.5\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\be1\an8}I'm not sure what it is but cheer up Yakumo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.15,0:15:27.12,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.53,0:15:31.73,SR-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBFBFBF&}It seems that Yakumo can hear Tenma's heart too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.68,0:15:33.74,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like it to be?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.45,0:15:38.88,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna write down my favorite ingredients, and Yakumo, you get to choose!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.75,0:15:40.50,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.01,0:15:43.13,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, pick!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.26,0:15:46.40,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnShannon\c&HF0F0F&}{\move(500,2,300,2)\q2\bord1.5\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\be1\an8}Left hand is ketchup. Right hand is banana daifuku.
