Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.62,0:16:05.16,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Never! Yay, yay! Banana daifuku curry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.46,0:16:05.16,SR-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBFBFBF&\a6}But to Yakumo, her sister is someone she would never scold.
