Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.52,0:16:14.14,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Itadakimasu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.10,0:16:16.97,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuck!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.60,0:16:20.17,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I think it's pretty good!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.47,0:16:25.47,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought dinner.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.40,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not here?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.35,0:17:04.46,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing, you can't get down right? Come here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.97,0:17:09.29,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. Slowly. Just a bit more.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.01,0:17:25.81,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.20,0:17:30.20,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ok?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.39,0:17:35.68,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnShannon\c&HF0F0F&}{\move(450,2,350,2)\q2\bord1.5\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\be1\an8}{\t(0,1300,\alpha&HFF&)}Meow {\alpha&HFF&\t(1000,2300,\alpha&H00&)}Meow {\alpha&HFF&\t(2000,3300,\alpha&H00&)}Meow
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.90,0:17:37.94,SR-Main,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.57,0:17:43.10,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I've been able to hear people's hearts,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.40,0:17:47.43,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always wondering what your thoughts would sound like.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.06,0:17:52.67,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess, in the end, cats go "meow meow" in their hearts, huh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.72,0:17:54.60,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.96,0:18:09.73,SR-Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Drats, I forgot my umbrella.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.02,0:18:11.97,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No big deal. Let's run for it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.97,0:18:15.98,SR-Main,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,It was sunny out earlier.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.58,0:18:17.76,SR-Main,MIko,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring an umbrella?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.11,SR-Main,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.11,0:18:21.11,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we can share mine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.90,SR-Main,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. What about you Akira?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.00,SR-Main,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,I have one.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.00,0:18:31.79,SR-Main,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is it okay not to wait for Tsukamoto? She said she had some plans, but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.48,0:18:37.62,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am definitely sure she didn't bring an umbrella. Positive.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.10,0:18:41.15,SR-Main,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I am sure Tenma has one.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.71,0:18:43.54,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's okay to go on ahead.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.21,0:18:45.54,SR-Main,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.10,0:18:46.97,SR-Main,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.49,0:18:50.30,SR-Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HCFCFCF&}Anyways I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.82,0:18:50.99,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Everyone left!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.87,0:18:54.37,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko-chan, you're so naive!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.87,0:18:56.95,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I didnt bring an umbrella, but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.72,0:18:58.86,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.70,0:19:03.00,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo brought me one anyways!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.68,0:19:05.68,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pouring hard.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.84,0:19:11.39,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry everyone. I don't really have plans.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.83,0:19:14.70,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't give this up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.87,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.87,0:19:21.37,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been waiting for this rainy day.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.78,0:19:24.31,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Today I shall not fail!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.00,0:19:27.35,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will share an umbrella with Karasuma-kun!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.56,0:19:30.56,SR-notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\b1\bord1.8\fs26}Translator's Note: {\b0}This theme of boy-girl sharing an umbrella is so big that in Japan, there's even a word for it: "Ai-ai-gasa"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.88,0:19:30.73,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait Karasuma-kun!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.87,0:19:40.54,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! If Karasuma-kun brought his own umbrella, it will be pointless!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.02,0:19:42.89,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I have overlooked such an essential thing...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.89,0:19:45.88,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I, how could I, how could I?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.09,0:19:45.88,SR-Main,karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HCDF2F5&}That hurts.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.42,0:19:53.28,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.24,0:19:53.28,SR-Main,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HCDF2F5&}It's okay. I'm fine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.71,0:19:59.13,SR-Main,TEnma,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, by the way, I wanted to ask you if...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.03,0:20:02.33,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...you have an umbrella?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.50,0:20:04.50,SR-Main,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.10,0:20:07.90,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,YES!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.28,0:20:10.79,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I have an umbrella!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.26,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, perhaps we can share it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.68,0:20:15.74,SR-Main,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,I have a raincoat.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.36,0:20:17.16,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Rain... !?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.91,0:20:23.23,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain... Raincoat!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.05,0:20:27.83,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A high school student wearing a raincoat in this era!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.49,0:20:29.83,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it Karasuma-kun!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.36,0:20:34.15,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That you are different from the common boys in many senses.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.11,0:20:36.77,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I like you so much.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.19,0:20:38.98,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what should I do?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.44,0:20:42.86,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't share an umbrella with him like this!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.97,0:20:47.74,SR-Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if you have an umbrella! Let's share one!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.17,0:20:51.87,SR-Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you wanna do that? We'll get wet with only one umbrella!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.97,0:20:57.92,SR-Main,gir,0000,0000,0000,,So what! I've always wanted to try it! Come on, it'll be fun.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.98,0:20:58.99,SR-Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.50,0:21:01.53,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I got it! There's also this way!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.19,0:21:04.35,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can try to talk him into doing it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.13,0:21:08.59,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun! I have a favor to ask!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.27,0:21:16.23,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you share an umbrella with me? I would be really happy... I mean I'm sure it'll be fun!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.73,0:21:36.73,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kappa...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.23,0:21:31.20,SR-notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\b1\bord1.8\fs26}Translator's Note: {\b0}Karasuma said he had a "kappa". A "kappa" usually means a "raincoat" but can also be a legendary frog demon.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.58,0:21:39.45,SR-Main,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I love it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.08,0:21:43.38,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun, even if you're a Kappa I still...love you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.31,0:21:51.86,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys are always, always...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.52,0:21:54.11,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,...Chasing after girls.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.23,0:21:57.82,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,All day long, always thinking...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.48,0:22:00.07,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,...About girls.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.15,0:22:04.58,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, boys are still so silly.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.58,0:22:07.58,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,See? They don't understand at all...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.58,0:22:09.38,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,...How the girls feel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.66,0:22:14.38,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, you silly silly guy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.87,0:22:17.30,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I reveal it to you, you silly guy?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.46,0:22:20.84,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The most important thing is this world,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.84,0:22:23.76,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing you absolutely cannot take for granted,{}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.76,0:22:28.05,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's the timing after all, isn't it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.26,0:22:31.22,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! When you say "I love you"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.22,0:22:34.36,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Or when you're on a date, or no matter what you're doing
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.27,0:22:37.10,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, when you're kissing too
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.10,0:22:40.36,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,When you say goodbye too, no matter when it is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.11,0:22:44.53,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The most important thing in this world is...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.53,0:22:48.92,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's timing, isn't it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.28,0:22:50.45,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,0)}Or is it so?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.54,0:23:09.75,SR-Main,tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Eh!? Softball? I'm so not good at sports.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.75,0:23:12.24,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But Karasuma-kun is watching me! I must do my best!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.52,0:23:13.83,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode on School Rumble!
